implementation_steps.step:
定义 change_processes 数组：
```json
{
  "id": "consciousness_raising",
  "name": "意识唤醒",
  "description": "提供信息增强对问题行为的认知",
  "primary_stages": ["precontemplation"]
},
{
  "id": "dramatic_relief",
  "name": "情感唤起",
  "description": "体验并表达与问题行为相关的情绪",
  "primary_stages": ["precontemplation", "contemplation"]
},
{
  "id": "self_reevaluation",
  "name": "自我再评价",
  "description": "评估改变对自我身份的正面影响",
  "primary_stages": ["contemplation"]
},
{
  "id": "environmental_reevaluation",
  "name": "环境再评价",
  "description": "评估问题行为对社会环境的影响",
  "primary_stages": ["contemplation"]
},
{
  "id": "self_liberation",
  "name": "自我解放",
  "description": "做出改变的承诺和选择",
  "primary_stages": ["preparation"]
},
{
  "id": "social_liberation",
  "name": "社会解放",
  "description": "增加社会替代方案",
  "primary_stages": ["preparation"]
},
{
  "id": "counterconditioning",
  "name": "反条件作用",
  "description": "用健康行为替代问题行为",
  "primary_stages": ["action"]
},
{
  "id": "stimulus_control",
  "name": "刺激控制",
  "description": "移除问题行为诱因，增加健康行为提示",
  "primary_stages": ["action"]
},
{
  "id": "reinforcement_management",
  "name": "强化管理",
  "description": "对积极改变提供奖励",
  "primary_stages": ["action", "maintenance"]
},
{
  "id": "helping_relationships",
  "name": "支持关系",
  "description": "利用社会支持维持改变",
  "primary_stages": ["maintenance"]
}
]
```

每个 process 包含：id, name, description, primary_stages（该过程最有效的阶段）
